WEBVTT

00:00:13.220 --> 00:00:21.180
Today is the day we are celebrating Easter.

00:00:21.180 --> 00:00:36.180
Easter is extremely symbolic, of - not only
of Christ, but also for all of us.

00:00:36.180 --> 00:00:49.660
In that the most important day is that of
resurrection.

00:00:49.660 --> 00:01:06.370
The resurrection of Christ has
the message of Christianity, not the cross.

00:01:06.370 --> 00:01:21.210
Through resurrection Christ had shown that
one can be resurrected with the body that

00:01:21.210 --> 00:01:26.010
you have.

00:01:26.010 --> 00:01:37.240
And without His resurrection, we could not
have managed the crossing of Agnya chakra,

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:41.550
no doubt.

00:01:41.550 --> 00:01:54.500
His life was very short of, we can say three
and half years only, He lived there.

00:01:54.500 --> 00:02:04.730
He came to India and He met Shalivahana, and
Shalivahana asked His name.

00:02:04.730 --> 00:02:06.800
He told him His name was Isa Masih.

00:02:06.800 --> 00:02:16.010
But He said, "I am coming from the country
where there are malichchas, mala-ichchha.

00:02:16.010 --> 00:02:26.630
They have ichchha of mal, desire to get dirty,
and I don't know how to live there.

00:02:26.630 --> 00:02:29.820
To Me, this is My country."

00:02:29.820 --> 00:02:40.150
But Shalivahana said that, "You should go
back and save Your people and give them Parama

00:02:40.150 --> 00:02:42.280
Nirmala Tattwam.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:50.980
So He went back, and as it is, within three
and half years He was crucified.

00:02:50.980 --> 00:03:02.960
At the time of His death He said so many beautiful
things for forgiveness, but ultimately He

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:07.310
said "Behold the Mother."

00:03:07.310 --> 00:03:09.960
That means you should hope for the Mother.

00:03:09.960 --> 00:03:23.030
And in His lifetime He also said that, "I'll
send you the Holy Ghost Who will comfort you,

00:03:23.030 --> 00:03:29.880
counsel you and also redeem", means resurrect
you.

00:03:29.880 --> 00:03:38.610
All these things He had said it because He
knew what was the whole plan.

00:03:38.610 --> 00:03:48.180
Also He said that, "You may say anything against
Me or do anything against Me, but anything

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:55.520
against the Holy Ghost I will not tolerate.

00:03:55.520 --> 00:04:00.370
I will not tolerate at any cost."

00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:09.360
Which is true also, so it is very dangerous
also to go against the Holy Ghost.

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.810
No doubt about it.

00:04:11.810 --> 00:04:19.670
It's not Me that is dangerous, but these Deities
are extremely dangerous.

00:04:19.670 --> 00:04:29.940
So, in Sahaja Yoga you are all resurrected
with your body.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:37.960
Before this you were not connected to the
All Pervading Power, and whatever you did

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:44.080
was through your mind or through your emotions.

00:04:44.080 --> 00:05:02.450
But you did not come out of that grave of
emotions and your desires, your actions and

00:05:02.450 --> 00:05:05.530
your ego.

00:05:05.530 --> 00:05:12.930
After realization now you know how free you
have become.

00:05:12.930 --> 00:05:26.530
How you have developed your own personality.

00:05:26.530 --> 00:05:38.450
There are so many instances which we can talk
about Christ, that He said, "Know Thyself"

00:05:38.450 --> 00:05:39.520
throughout.

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:43.960
He knew without knowing yourself, you won't
be resurrected.

00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:48.290
But Sahaja Yoga is the other way round.

00:05:48.290 --> 00:05:53.880
You get your resurrection and you know yourself.

00:05:53.880 --> 00:06:02.740
It's a very Sahaja, sweet way of getting realization.

00:06:02.740 --> 00:06:12.580
But if you see to the life of Christ, He has
talked about murmuring souls.

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:18.080
We too have in Sahaja Yoga, because it's open
to everyone, all kinds of people come.

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:28.830
We find very shallow people coming to Sahaja
Yoga who try to express their shallowness

00:06:28.830 --> 00:06:41.310
and talk in a very, in a very
loose way, about Sahaja Yoga, about the work

00:06:41.310 --> 00:06:44.210
of Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:44.210 --> 00:06:52.480
So that was inevitable, but what Christ has
said that you have to be careful about the

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:55.440
murmuring souls.

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:59.330
And this is exactly - we have to be very careful.

00:06:59.330 --> 00:07:06.420
When you come to Sahaja Yoga, in the beginning,
you may come across such people who are murmuring

00:07:06.420 --> 00:07:20.110
souls, you may be enticed by them because
they are a kind of, we should say, messengers

00:07:20.110 --> 00:07:22.800
of negative forces.

00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:28.430
And these messengers of negative forces, you
should try to find out.

00:07:28.430 --> 00:07:34.890
They'll complain about this, complain about
that, they talk in a very loose manner, and

00:07:34.890 --> 00:07:48.210
when you see that they are not talking in
a positive way, you should run away from them.

00:07:48.210 --> 00:07:54.670
Because only by getting your resurrection
you are not all right.

00:07:54.670 --> 00:08:00.680
After getting your resurrection, after your
Self-realization, you have to grow.

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:10.600
And for that growth we have to be very careful
about how we get impressed by all these, I

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:14.510
should say, very frivolous people.

00:08:14.510 --> 00:08:21.170
Those who grow into it become beautiful angels.

00:08:21.170 --> 00:08:24.160
No doubt about that.

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:29.760
But that is one thing one has to know is to
respect your Self-realization.

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:34.700
You shouldn't worry about what others are
talking, what others are saying, what they

00:08:34.700 --> 00:08:42.520
are criticizing, but you should look at yourself
and all the time try to grow into your depth.

00:08:42.520 --> 00:08:48.370
It's a very great chance of life that you
are being resurrected, and this is the last

00:08:48.370 --> 00:08:51.890
breakthrough, as you know, of our evolution.

00:08:51.890 --> 00:08:58.330
But now you should leave your mind on one
side; because this mind, if you go on working

00:08:58.330 --> 00:09:05.830
with it, you cannot go beyond mind and Sahaja
Yoga you can achieve by going beyond your

00:09:05.830 --> 00:09:08.100
mind.

00:09:08.100 --> 00:09:13.350
Then you know yourself, because you get Self-knowledge.

00:09:13.350 --> 00:09:16.030
You know about your centers.

00:09:16.030 --> 00:09:18.110
You know about the centers of others.

00:09:18.110 --> 00:09:26.800
All this is available to you, but you have
to become a subtler and subtler person.

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:28.270
Not a gross personality.

00:09:28.270 --> 00:09:37.420
If you become subtler and subtler, you will
be amazed how you will develop your inner

00:09:37.420 --> 00:09:42.870
powers in so many different ways.

00:09:42.870 --> 00:09:48.850
But there are people in Sahaja Yoga, I have
seen, who are very ambitious.

00:09:48.850 --> 00:09:54.700
And they start saying that, "Mother, we want
to be God realized.

00:09:54.700 --> 00:09:57.400
I want to be this and do that."

00:09:57.400 --> 00:10:03.220
There is no office going on here that you
give somebody a promotion.

00:10:03.220 --> 00:10:06.470
You have to grow yourself.

00:10:06.470 --> 00:10:11.360
Then they start proclaiming, "I am this, I
am that."

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:13.540
We call them 'Mahayogis'.

00:10:13.540 --> 00:10:18.890
Some of them had started saying that they
have reached very high positions and they

00:10:18.890 --> 00:10:23.400
ended up in the lunatic asylum.

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:32.040
All such suggestions if people give you, then
you should shun such people.

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:39.220
But there are also other people who join such
a bombastic fellow.

00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:50.010
So, you must remember that this last judgment
is working and all the time there is a big

00:10:50.010 --> 00:10:59.870
sieving out, a very big arrangement of choices.

00:10:59.870 --> 00:11:05.370
Those who are subtle, start getting subtler
and subtler and subtler.

00:11:05.370 --> 00:11:15.580
But those who are frivolous, gross, idiotic,
stupid, they start frittering away.

00:11:15.580 --> 00:11:25.290
So this last sieving starts very fast, working
out where we realize that where are we.

00:11:25.290 --> 00:11:30.910
Now what is the criteria for that?

00:11:30.910 --> 00:11:37.550
First is your compassion.

00:11:37.550 --> 00:11:44.640
Your compassion must be discrete.

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:49.200
Sometimes people only have compassion for
negative people.

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:58.200
After Sahaja Yoga you should know for whom
you should have your compassion.

00:11:58.200 --> 00:12:05.820
With vibrations you can find out, very easy
to find out with vibrations - what sort of

00:12:05.820 --> 00:12:07.920
a person you are facing.

00:12:07.920 --> 00:12:12.330
But first you must have vibratory awareness.

00:12:12.330 --> 00:12:24.350
If you don't have vibratory awareness, you
won't be able to find out at all what is correct

00:12:24.350 --> 00:12:26.290
and what is incorrect.

00:12:26.290 --> 00:12:32.990
So it is important that you all must mediate.

00:12:32.990 --> 00:12:37.790
Without criticizing yourself, anything, you
can just meditate everyday.

00:12:37.790 --> 00:12:39.160
Is very important!

00:12:39.160 --> 00:12:47.710
I immediately know who is the person who is
meditating and who is not meditating.

00:12:47.710 --> 00:12:48.710
Immediately!

00:12:48.710 --> 00:12:58.100
The person who meditates is very clearly an
angel.

00:12:58.100 --> 00:13:09.940
The whole reaction, the whole behavior, the
whole attitude of such spiritual maturity

00:13:09.940 --> 00:13:11.740
manifests.

00:13:11.740 --> 00:13:16.160
And you are amazed.

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:20.050
As you know Sahasrare Mahamaya.

00:13:20.050 --> 00:13:23.220
It's not easy to understand Me.

00:13:23.220 --> 00:13:31.430
For the time being you might know what I am,
but suddenly you will forget.

00:13:31.430 --> 00:13:34.060
That's the trick.

00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:38.720
Because if you know Me in full ways, you won't
even sit here.

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:42.660
You won't even come nearer to Me.

00:13:42.660 --> 00:13:51.610
So that Mahamaya is acting all the time, but
that's the only way you can judge people.

00:13:51.610 --> 00:13:55.560
This last judgment is not a easy thing.

00:13:55.560 --> 00:14:00.180
Even if you put thousands of judges, they
cannot do this judgment.

00:14:00.180 --> 00:14:07.870
All the time you have to know what is what.

00:14:07.870 --> 00:14:15.000
And somehow I know everything, but I will
never show that I know.

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:24.170
That's how I work it out, and gradually I
know what I have to do about that person.

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:33.030
This resurrection of yours is much more blessed
than that of Christ.

00:14:33.030 --> 00:14:37.730
He was alone; people wouldn't recognize Him.

00:14:37.730 --> 00:14:45.110
He had to show His marks where they had put
nails on His hands and feet.

00:14:45.110 --> 00:14:48.650
But today that is not the situation.

00:14:48.650 --> 00:14:55.230
Only thing is, first of all you have to recognize
Me.

00:14:55.230 --> 00:14:56.550
That's all.

00:14:56.550 --> 00:14:58.500
Need not know Me.

00:14:58.500 --> 00:14:59.500
It's not easy.

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:05.390
It's difficult to know Me, but if you recognize
Me, that's all.

00:15:05.390 --> 00:15:09.310
And it all depends on your sensitivity.

00:15:09.310 --> 00:15:18.840
Your resurrection has to be complete and you
have to mature in Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:23.840
If you cannot mature, I will say you should
leave Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:32.580
Go out for a while, where you will understand
what's going on, then you'll come back.

00:15:32.580 --> 00:15:44.830
In Sahaja Yoga, like Christ sacrificed His
life, is not expected of you to sacrifice

00:15:44.830 --> 00:15:45.830
your life.

00:15:45.830 --> 00:15:48.720
Your Mother doesn't want that.

00:15:48.720 --> 00:15:59.320
But you have to do some sacrifices, like you
have to stay in uncomfortable places in Ganapatipule

00:15:59.320 --> 00:16:01.340
sometimes, or somewhere.

00:16:01.340 --> 00:16:12.670
You have to face many odds while traveling,
also coming down here may not be so comfortable

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:16.390
as you are at your place.

00:16:16.390 --> 00:16:21.610
But the main sacrifice is of your ego.

00:16:21.610 --> 00:16:23.680
You have to crucify your ego.

00:16:23.680 --> 00:16:34.110
The ego is the one, which teaches you all
these nonsensical tantrums that people know.

00:16:34.110 --> 00:16:45.820
If you can surrender your ego - just surrender
your ego - that surrendering can help you.

00:16:45.820 --> 00:16:55.960
But if you surrender your ego by thinking
about it, then you are using your mental capacity.

00:16:55.960 --> 00:17:02.490
Everything you do like that is through your
mental capacity, by which you are using your

00:17:02.490 --> 00:17:04.770
ego.

00:17:04.770 --> 00:17:13.180
So the best way is to meditate, to go into
thoughtless awareness and there automatically

00:17:13.180 --> 00:17:14.870
you are surrendered.

00:17:14.870 --> 00:17:17.770
Now what do I have to have from you?

00:17:17.770 --> 00:17:18.770
Nothing!

00:17:18.770 --> 00:17:19.770
I don't want anything.

00:17:19.770 --> 00:17:21.910
I don't want to have anything.

00:17:21.910 --> 00:17:24.630
You are the ones who try to give Me this and
give Me that.

00:17:24.630 --> 00:17:28.110
I am trying to run away from all that.

00:17:28.110 --> 00:17:33.720
Just for your satisfaction also, I agree.

00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:41.670
I don't have to do Sahaja Yoga Myself, but
that's the love of your Mother.

00:17:41.670 --> 00:17:50.930
That She wants to save as many as possible
- all that are created on this Earth - to

00:17:50.930 --> 00:17:51.930
give them their resurrection.

00:17:51.930 --> 00:17:56.840
This is a special time and you are My channels.

00:17:56.840 --> 00:18:06.170
You can go all over and spread Sahaja Yoga
and try to help others to come out of it.

00:18:06.170 --> 00:18:14.670
Today is a day of promises, where we have
to promise ourselves that we'll grow in a

00:18:14.670 --> 00:18:26.650
very deeper understanding, or feeling, or
in sensitiveness of Sahaja Yoga.

00:18:26.650 --> 00:18:34.100
This growth has to take place for which I
have to meditate.

00:18:34.100 --> 00:18:36.700
This is a very important thing.

00:18:36.700 --> 00:18:44.160
Secondly, people say that here people are
very miserly.

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:46.380
They are not willing to do this.

00:18:46.380 --> 00:18:51.020
They don't want to pay any money for this,
pay any money for that.

00:18:51.020 --> 00:18:55.270
I think generosity is one expression of your
love.

00:18:55.270 --> 00:18:57.490
You will give Me, all right.

00:18:57.490 --> 00:19:04.440
When it comes to expenses, either I pay or
somebody bears the burden.

00:19:04.440 --> 00:19:12.130
Now things have improved, but still we should
know that this tremendous work has to be done

00:19:12.130 --> 00:19:14.880
and we need money for that.

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:18.540
I don't need, I spend My own money.

00:19:18.540 --> 00:19:29.490
But generosity is the best and this generosity
is very, very important for Sahaja Yogis.

00:19:29.490 --> 00:19:35.100
I have seen people are very meticulous sometimes,
very calculating.

00:19:35.100 --> 00:19:39.320
They will tell Me, "Bring some sarees for
them."

00:19:39.320 --> 00:19:41.310
Take some sarees, all right, very good idea.

00:19:41.310 --> 00:19:44.210
And they say, "We don't like it, we don't
want to buy."

00:19:44.210 --> 00:19:46.700
I am not doing any business.

00:19:46.700 --> 00:19:51.600
I buy it because you wanted, I have selected
it.

00:19:51.600 --> 00:19:53.730
Then to say, "we don't want to have it."

00:19:53.730 --> 00:19:58.240
There's no business, there's no marketing
going on.

00:19:58.240 --> 00:20:05.260
And this is the problem when I don't understand
Sahaja Yogis that they should know Mother,

00:20:05.260 --> 00:20:08.090
Herself, has put in Her money.

00:20:08.090 --> 00:20:14.960
So what is there also, they should say, "take
little more for Sahaja Yoga."

00:20:14.960 --> 00:20:20.860
After all such a big organization going on,
and there are so many countries who cannot

00:20:20.860 --> 00:20:25.740
pay a single farthing, for them also one has
to pay.

00:20:25.740 --> 00:20:30.180
Now, Christ was sold for thirty rubles.

00:20:30.180 --> 00:20:35.030
You can imagine, He was sold for thirty rubles.

00:20:35.030 --> 00:20:44.090
So that shows that when you do not try to
understand the financial difficulties of the

00:20:44.090 --> 00:20:52.630
organizers and you do not help, you are really
selling the Christ within you.

00:20:52.630 --> 00:21:00.690
You cannot sell Christ, you cannot sell Sahaja
Yoga.

00:21:00.690 --> 00:21:04.210
But that doesn't mean you exploit it.

00:21:04.210 --> 00:21:10.250
So I have to tell you that I was Myself surprised
in north India where I least expected people

00:21:10.250 --> 00:21:15.090
are extremely generous, extremely generous.

00:21:15.090 --> 00:21:27.030
And then generosity helps you, in a way that
our Lakshmi Tatwa is to be awakened.

00:21:27.030 --> 00:21:33.620
I had to bring in this point because I have
complaints from people that people are reluctant

00:21:33.620 --> 00:21:38.190
to pay for anything like this.

00:21:38.190 --> 00:21:48.270
It's very remarkable that some people take
over, but everybody must contribute.

00:21:48.270 --> 00:21:52.440
It's important, because you are doing God's
work.

00:21:52.440 --> 00:21:57.780
You have to also come forward to do other
things that are there without grudging.

00:21:57.780 --> 00:21:59.300
Enjoying it!

00:21:59.300 --> 00:22:06.770
I was happy the posters were put by the Sahaja
Yogis, and you can see the whole place vibrated.

00:22:06.770 --> 00:22:11.460
You could see how it has worked out.

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:18.390
So everybody must go all out to do everything
that is possible.

00:22:18.390 --> 00:22:25.920
Nothing else is needed but your full heart
into Sahaja Yoga.

00:22:25.920 --> 00:22:28.410
Then you will see how you will grow.

00:22:28.410 --> 00:22:34.100
It is only through your heart you will receive
all your nourishment for your spirituality.

00:22:34.300 --> 00:22:38.710
So open your heart,
do not calculate so much.

00:22:41.400 --> 00:22:45.750
I have to speak to you in Hindi, very important.

00:22:46.150 --> 00:22:50.340
Good wishes to you all for today.

00:22:50.660 --> 00:22:53.820
On this day Isa Masih [Jesus Christ]

00:22:54.080 --> 00:23:03.140
came of the dead world and He was Resurrected with His body.

00:23:03.370 --> 00:23:09.510
In the same way your Resurrection has happened with the body, not after death.

00:23:09.710 --> 00:23:13.580
But now
when you are alive.

00:23:13.800 --> 00:23:17.790
In the living state itself you got your Resurrection.

00:23:18.010 --> 00:23:23.030
But there are some significance of Resurrection that you need to understand.

00:23:23.240 --> 00:23:27.670
After Resurrection you should develop sensitivity.

00:23:27.870 --> 00:23:31.870
If you still have the thoughts of doing business in Sahaja Yoga,

00:23:32.070 --> 00:23:38.700
or making money, or fulfilling desires, then you have come on the wrong path.

00:23:39.060 --> 00:23:41.060
You should go elsewhere.

00:23:41.230 --> 00:23:46.760
In Sahaja Yoga, you should only think of spiritual upliftment.

00:23:47.320 --> 00:23:52.360
Other than that, there should not be any thoughts. But now everyone asked,

00:23:52.560 --> 00:23:58.730
“Mother, why the Lakshmi principle of Bengal doesn’t get awakened?”

00:23:59.160 --> 00:24:02.520
The reason is because there are many tantriks [black magicians] here.

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:08.580
Wherever tantriks [black magicians] come, Lakshmiji goes away from those places.

00:24:08.780 --> 00:24:12.650
Not just that even with alcohol it’s the same.

00:24:12.840 --> 00:24:18.950
For some time it’s ok, but after some time due to alcohol, Lakshmi will go away.

00:24:19.180 --> 00:24:21.370
It is against Lakshmi.

00:24:21.840 --> 00:24:26.270
The number of tantriks [black magicians] that are there in Bengal are nowhere.

00:24:26.470 --> 00:24:31.940
While trying to find the reason I understand that people of Bengal are very

00:24:32.140 --> 00:24:37.640
tolerant and emotional.

00:24:38.510 --> 00:24:44.900
And any person who comes and tells them that he is godly person, they believe him.

00:24:45.100 --> 00:24:47.640
They don’t think about it.

00:24:48.050 --> 00:24:52.370
Like the movement of ‘Hare Rama’ started from Bengal.

00:24:52.570 --> 00:24:56.300
Like mad people they ran on the streets, running everywhere -

00:24:56.500 --> 00:24:58.870
“Hare Ram, Hare Ram, Hare Ram, Hare Ram”.

00:24:59.070 --> 00:25:03.400
How did they benefit?
More poverty came in.

00:25:04.430 --> 00:25:08.860
If anyone says anything, people of Bengal start doing it.

00:25:09.060 --> 00:25:14.020
Someone told me, “I don’t eat green coriander leaves” I asked, “Why?”

00:25:14.220 --> 00:25:18.230
“My elder sister stopped eating green coriander leaves, so I also left it”.

00:25:18.470 --> 00:25:21.530
“But why,
why did your sister stop?”

00:25:21.730 --> 00:25:27.130
Such rituals they get stuck in.

00:25:27.500 --> 00:25:33.070
Living by those rituals, we get lost.

00:25:34.690 --> 00:25:36.690
Totally lost.

00:25:37.050 --> 00:25:42.580
About those rituals, we need to understand the reasoning behind it.

00:25:42.780 --> 00:25:47.320
In Sahaja Yoga, there is not ritual, no religion,

00:25:47.670 --> 00:25:53.120
no preaching of any religion.

00:25:53.540 --> 00:25:55.900
And the most important thing,

00:25:56.100 --> 00:26:02.760
the world brotherhood (collectivity) comes from within, is established from the heart.

00:26:04.070 --> 00:26:11.500
The day we get this feeling in us, we can drive away the tantriks [black magicians].

00:26:11.700 --> 00:26:19.600
If one Sahaja Yogi desires, then he can drive away all the tantriks [black magicians] by his powers.

00:26:19.830 --> 00:26:23.880
There is a place named Girgaon in Mumbai.

00:26:24.200 --> 00:26:29.790
A devi [here it means dead spirit] used to possess people. This devi would possess and dance.

00:26:29.990 --> 00:26:37.140
One Sahaja Yogini went there, after that it stopped. The persons dancing stopped; she ran away.

00:26:37.420 --> 00:26:42.760
Because Godly Powers are very much higher than worldly powers.

00:26:43.130 --> 00:26:47.400
When you are awakened and then when you become pure,

00:26:47.600 --> 00:26:54.650
when you become ‘Nirmal’ [spotless], the inner power of purity starts working.

00:26:54.970 --> 00:26:59.560
So it is required of the Sahaja Yogis that they make themselves pure.

00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:04.470
We get pleased in devotion, we get into the game of intelligence.

00:27:04.670 --> 00:27:05.700
All that is fine.

00:27:05.910 --> 00:27:12.100
You have to be delighted.
But most importantly look into oneself.

00:27:13.110 --> 00:27:16.000
Increase the power within you.

00:27:16.230 --> 00:27:18.800
The day you all increase your powers,

00:27:19.030 --> 00:27:24.330
all tantriks [black magicians] will take their belongings and go away.

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:26.660
That is why,

00:27:26.970 --> 00:27:31.730
today on the day of Resurrection
take an oath in your mind

00:27:31.940 --> 00:27:36.700
that we will become deep Sahaja Yogis
of the highest order.

00:27:37.300 --> 00:27:40.350
Sahaja Yogis who have depth.

00:27:40.840 --> 00:27:46.670
For that if you have to meditate; now it doesn’t mean that you meditate for 3 hours.

00:27:46.870 --> 00:27:50.340
But for ten minutes,
you meditate from the heart.

00:27:50.540 --> 00:27:54.620
From the heart is very important.
There is so much of compassion in Bengal,

00:27:54.820 --> 00:27:59.670
so much of loving feeling,

00:28:00.090 --> 00:28:02.960
but see the role.

00:28:03.410 --> 00:28:07.520
If you are a Sahaja Yogi,
first you have to love yourself.

00:28:07.720 --> 00:28:14.530
As soon as you love yourself you’ll find
that your love will spread everywhere.

00:28:14.830 --> 00:28:16.730
You get angry,

00:28:17.400 --> 00:28:19.400
you have desires.

00:28:19.740 --> 00:28:25.870
There are some more
titles attached to you

00:28:26.170 --> 00:28:29.040
and you are Sahaja Yogi also.

00:28:29.600 --> 00:28:33.640
Cleansing of all these only,
is your Resurrection.

00:28:33.840 --> 00:28:39.280
When your personality
is complete after cleansing,

00:28:39.510 --> 00:28:44.280
then no tantric can remain here.
Never can they remain.

00:28:44.730 --> 00:28:47.580
The other thing I told was that,

00:28:47.790 --> 00:28:52.300
that you have such beautiful
melodious way of singing.

00:28:52.710 --> 00:28:58.380
So some ladies and men can hire a big

00:28:58.880 --> 00:29:03.720
[Shri Mataji speaks aside: Son later, later, later, ok?].

00:29:04.550 --> 00:29:06.550
Hire any

00:29:08.250 --> 00:29:11.170
bus, a truck or anything

00:29:11.380 --> 00:29:16.400
and announce in the villages that here there will be bhajan of Shri Mataji.

00:29:16.600 --> 00:29:19.210
You reach the village

00:29:19.710 --> 00:29:28.190
and sing songs, give a discourse.

00:29:28.980 --> 00:29:31.590
Slowly play My tapes.

00:29:31.790 --> 00:29:35.110
Like this, in north India, many people got Realization.

00:29:35.310 --> 00:29:43.620
Entire UP, Bihar, Haryana everywhere Sahaja Yoga has spread completely.

00:29:43.960 --> 00:29:49.610
That I have seen when you have the power of singing,

00:29:49.890 --> 00:29:52.770
why not go to the villages

00:29:52.970 --> 00:30:01.270
and awaken people by singing and Resurrect them?

00:30:01.720 --> 00:30:05.910
By doing this all tantriks [people who practice black magic] will run away.

00:30:06.110 --> 00:30:10.370
With My name itself they start shaking, then if you sing My songs,

00:30:10.570 --> 00:30:14.140
you don’t know what all you can achieve.

00:30:14.340 --> 00:30:21.020
The wisdom is that the love you have received from Mother, has to be distributed.

00:30:21.310 --> 00:30:29.390
And in this place there is so much need for love in the people.

00:30:29.750 --> 00:30:32.330
You go and see, meet them.

00:30:32.530 --> 00:30:36.030
Just by you being there, Lakshmi will come there.

00:30:36.240 --> 00:30:40.750
By your living there everyone’s physical body also will become alright;

00:30:40.950 --> 00:30:43.210
psychologically they will become alright;

00:30:43.410 --> 00:30:48.590
prosperity will be there and most importantly the spirituality will be set right.

00:30:48.800 --> 00:30:53.000
In this way we have to change the people of our country.

00:30:53.200 --> 00:30:57.360
But for that you will have to work.

00:30:57.920 --> 00:31:05.580
Today is so significant that it shows how human beings in their living body,

00:31:05.780 --> 00:31:11.240
can achieve Resurrection, like how Isa Masih [Jesus Christ] had done.

00:31:11.440 --> 00:31:16.630
But the Power which Isa Masih [Jesus Christ] had is beyond our reach.

00:31:16.830 --> 00:31:23.280
He had told that if you do something wrong with one eye then remove the eye yourself.

00:31:23.480 --> 00:31:28.510
Then He said that if the hand does something wrong then cut off the hand.

00:31:28.710 --> 00:31:34.690
I have lived with many Christians of the world. I have seen many Christian countries

00:31:34.890 --> 00:31:40.320
but I haven’t seen even one person’s eyes removed or hand cut.

00:31:40.520 --> 00:31:43.300
Those people have ignored all that.

00:31:43.590 --> 00:31:48.580
Now you people should not become your own enemies. This is not there in Sahaja Yoga.

00:31:48.790 --> 00:31:54.900
You see the problems in you and if you really love yourself,

00:31:55.110 --> 00:32:01.950
getting rid of these problems is the way to achieve complete Resurrection.

00:32:02.350 --> 00:32:08.340
When these problems go away, then you will be surprised that how much of happiness,

00:32:08.540 --> 00:32:12.560
how much of peace
and how much of Power is residing.

00:32:12.760 --> 00:32:17.940
Those things that are coming in the way of you achieving this Power

00:32:18.300 --> 00:32:22.110
that somehow you have to give up.

00:32:22.340 --> 00:32:31.210
These obstacles come up because we don’t give much importance to our Resurrection.

00:32:31.410 --> 00:32:36.340
We give for other things.
All other thing are important.

00:32:36.540 --> 00:32:46.570
The Ressurection we have achieved, we see ourselves in a different level,

00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:56.110
where we have entered the Kingdom of God; to be seated there we have to clear ourselves.

00:32:56.450 --> 00:33:00.660
Finding satisfaction in other things is of no use.

00:33:00.860 --> 00:33:06.690
One says, “Our, this thing doesn’t happen”. Other says, “That doesn’t happen”. First of all

00:33:06.890 --> 00:33:11.560
you completely honor yourself,
respect yourself.

00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:19.890
By falling low, by going down a wrong path how can you become spiritual?

00:33:20.090 --> 00:33:24.380
And how will you get peace?
It’s very difficult.

00:33:24.590 --> 00:33:29.880
Those people who say, “We don’t have peace Mother, that’s why we do that, we do this”.

00:33:30.080 --> 00:33:35.990
Peace is not a difficult thing. If you do meditation and do all the work from your heart,

00:33:36.190 --> 00:33:40.270
from your heart,
then what is difficult?

00:33:40.470 --> 00:33:46.230
Nothing is difficult. In Sahaja Yoga some people have reached great heights from low level.

00:33:46.430 --> 00:33:49.930
I see that in their love there is so much of power.

00:33:50.130 --> 00:33:55.050
About one person I shall definitely describe to you today. One person

00:33:55.250 --> 00:33:59.670
was very much surrendered to Mother.

00:34:00.380 --> 00:34:09.050
We were at Prague airport, on the way.
We were going to Poland probably.

00:34:09.690 --> 00:34:17.720
So this person told us that the flight is scheduled to depart at 11.

00:34:18.230 --> 00:34:20.940
So we got ready accordingly and reached the airport.

00:34:21.140 --> 00:34:25.660
Then they said, “No, the flight is leaving early, 1 hour early, so you reach somehow”.

00:34:25.840 --> 00:34:30.450
How could we reach immediately? We go late by 15 minutes.

00:34:30.860 --> 00:34:37.310
The lady there, the ground hostess was an Austrian,

00:34:38.010 --> 00:34:43.340
because the flight was supposed to go to Austria first. She scolded us a lot,

00:34:43.540 --> 00:34:50.890
“You people are like this. You have no sense of time” and so on. We were listening quietly.

00:34:51.330 --> 00:34:55.820
Now this person could not bear it as he had told Me the wrong time.

00:34:56.020 --> 00:34:58.560
We went and sat in the flight.

00:34:58.760 --> 00:35:05.930
Once we sat in the plane, this poor emotional person, tears started rolling down his eyes.

00:35:06.130 --> 00:35:09.780
He’s a German, he started to cry.

00:35:10.020 --> 00:35:14.460
He was sitting behind. Other Sahaja Yogis were consoling him, “Be quiet, be quiet”.

00:35:14.660 --> 00:35:19.150
I looked at him once and I told him, “Now you calm down, it’s alright”.

00:35:19.350 --> 00:35:24.830
By then they told us that the plane will not leave as a problem has arisen.

00:35:25.030 --> 00:35:27.790
But the minute I saw tears in his eyes,

00:35:28.000 --> 00:35:33.830
black clouds emerged everywhere in the sky all of a sudden. The Sahaja Yogis were thinking

00:35:34.030 --> 00:35:39.550
from where did these black elephants [here - thick dark clouds] come from? Suddenly. See the power of his love.

00:35:39.750 --> 00:35:43.900
They told us, “You go back to the airport. The plane will not leave”.

00:35:44.100 --> 00:35:48.820
By the time we reached the airport, it started to rain very heavily.

00:35:49.100 --> 00:35:51.730
Not one plane could take off from there.

00:35:51.930 --> 00:35:56.010
Only our plane they said will leave by 5.00.
[break in recording]

00:35:56.220 --> 00:36:03.790
A lot of things are being done in Bengal but Bengal will improve only when you will go to the villages and work.

00:36:03.990 --> 00:36:06.790
Today I ask only this

00:36:07.150 --> 00:36:13.540
that all of you have been resurrected and now just sitting in Kolkata, it cannot be achieved.

00:36:13.740 --> 00:36:17.510
You have to go out and work.

00:36:17.720 --> 00:36:23.310
Till the time you do not spread this,

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:29.320
such a big precious thing,

00:36:29.770 --> 00:36:34.590
which will grow only by spreading, like knowledge.

00:36:34.950 --> 00:36:40.860
Knowledge increases by spreading, in the same way Sahaja Yoga will grow by spreading.

00:36:41.060 --> 00:36:45.190
And with this entire Bengal will be benefitted.

00:36:46.050 --> 00:36:51.280
It is surprising that so many people have come in Sahaja Yoga puja today.

00:36:51.480 --> 00:36:57.550
Felt very happy and I hope next time when I come

00:36:57.750 --> 00:37:01.300
you will bring a lot of people.

00:37:02.250 --> 00:37:08.330
This singing and art of yours, which is respected a lot,

00:37:08.930 --> 00:37:20.740
you use that and spread Sahaja Yoga in entire Bengal, through your singing.

00:37:21.260 --> 00:37:23.620
My blessings.